column5: I've passed by this area a few times wondering what exactly they do in the "experimental lakes" area. They've posted summaries from their yearly findings on the link below.  Personally I'd stock it with Musky and Pike, set up underwater cameras and sell videos called "Pike vs. Musky: battle royal" or "Pike vs. Musky : it'll knock esox off"  http://www.experimen.../Summaries.html
I like the second one. Quite witty.
